snippet: Rosenman--Phyllis, died March 30, 2014 after 94 full years of life. She was a devoted wife, mother, grandmother, great-grandmother, sister, aunt and mother-in-law. She will be forever missed....
lead_paragraph: Rosenman--Phyllis, died March 30, 2014 after 94 full years of life. She was a devoted wife, mother, grandmother, great-grandmother, sister, aunt and mother-in-law. She will be forever missed.
